title: Python Programming
details: Python is a high-level, general-purpose programming language. Its design philosophy emphasizes code readability with the use of significant indentation.Python is dynamically-typed and garbage-collected. It supports multiple programming paradigms, including structured (particularly procedural), object-oriented and functional programming. It is often described as a language due to its comprehensive standard library.Guido van Rossum began working on Python in the late 1980
